      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mushrooms are brown, reduce the heat to medium-high</p><p>Add a large knob of <strong>butter </strong>and your <strong>gochujang paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan with your <strong>soy sauce </strong>and the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>ginger paste</strong></p><p>Cook for 1 min or until the butter has melted</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1670924160128-x200.jpg",
