    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the noodles have warmed through, add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>grated cheese</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) and give everything a good mix up until the noodles are evenly coated – these are your <strong>cheesy gochujang udon noodles</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of<strong> </strong>water if it's looking a little dry</p>",
